{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading1.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>Ever dreamt of managing 1, maybe 2, who knows? Possibly a 100 pet shops! Now that's possible without the real life risk. Sell Pet food, Pet toys, a lot of accessories for pets and even breed pets. You can also find homes for stray pets.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading2.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>Want to have a plant, or a custom sign, maybe you want a wall there? Everything is possible because you can organise your stores the way you like!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading3.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>You can open so may stores (up to 15000 to be precise), the possibilities are endless. You can have a store in every part of the world!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading4.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>You should hire the right employees which won't steal from the cash register. Running 15000 pet shops may become overwhelming, but don't worry! You can always hire a manager!<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading5.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>Sign contracts with the best companies whose products people will buy! But be careful, there is a penalty if you don't sell enough products.<br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/extras/heading6.png?t=1699182910\" /><br>Go to the R&amp;D department and research everything from e-commerce to pets selling, everything is possible!","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2467890/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1699182910","background_raw":"https://